- Listen.

1053
00:46:54,490 --> 00:46:57,058
The theme they're going after is a bibim-style dish.

1054
00:46:57,059 --> 00:46:59,828
But I'm not entirely sure if the intention is...

1055
00:46:59,829 --> 00:47:02,089
