1057
00:47:06,099 --> 00:47:07,968
(Five-colour jjajang naengmyeon)

1058
00:47:07,969 --> 00:47:11,338
(No indication in Korean that it's served cold)

1059
00:47:11,339 --> 00:47:14,169
There will be people who like it and people who don't.

1060
00:47:14,369 --> 00:47:17,809
But at least 60 percent of the people will like the dish.

1061
00:47:18,539 --> 00:47:21,279
That's why I thought we'd be fine.

1062
00:47:23,479 --> 00:47:24,679
