1101
00:49:25,199 --> 00:49:26,768
- Whatever you want.
- Jjajang.

1102
00:49:26,769 --> 00:49:27,969
- Jjajang.
- Let's get jjajang.

1103
00:49:28,169 --> 00:49:29,478
- I came straight here.
- Really?

1104
00:49:29,479 --> 00:49:30,679
- I didn't look around.
- Why not?

1105
00:49:31,009 --> 00:49:32,138
I was set on jjajangmyeon.

1106
00:49:32,139 --> 00:49:33,379
- To get jjajangmyeon?
- I get it.

1107
00:49:34,079 --> 00:49:35,849
- Another order.
- Another one?

1108
00:49:36,179 --> 00:49:37,579
Let's move on after serving this one.

1109
00:49:38,649 --> 00:49:40,349
