- It's served quickly.

1139
00:51:02,069 --> 00:51:03,269
Like, "What's that?"

1140
00:51:03,369 --> 00:51:05,469
- Totally.
- Nice.

1141
00:51:07,369 --> 00:51:10,039
Alaskan pink shrimp avocado tartare sounds good.

1142
00:51:10,739 --> 00:51:12,948
(Impressed)

1143
00:51:12,949 --> 00:51:14,049
It looks amazing.

1144
00:51:14,809 --> 00:51:15,949
Oh, gosh.

1145
00:51:16,649 --> 00:51:19,449
That's a dish you can't find in Sejong.

1146
00:51:20,049 --> 00:51:21,489
It's avocado tartare.

1147
00:51:22,319 --> 00:51:23,388
- Should we get it?
- Yes.

1148
00:51:23,389 --> 00:51:24,519
I love avocado.

1149
00:51:25,159 --> 00:51:26,159
- Let's order it.
- Okay.

1150
00:51:26,929 --> 00:51:31,799
(Out of 30 customers, 29 were female groups.)

1151
00:51:32,159 --> 00:51:33,428
They know what tartare is.

1152
00:51:33,429 --> 00:51:34,498
Women know what tartare is.

1153
00:51:34,499 --> 00:51:35,829
- "It's tartare!" - Of course.

1154
00:51:36,199 --> 00:51:37,598
Men might not know it,

1155
00:51:37,599 --> 00:51:39,239
