1156
00:51:41,669 --> 00:51:42,909
Hi, did you order something?

1157
00:51:43,179 --> 00:51:44,379
Yes. What did you get?

1158
00:51:44,679 --> 00:51:46,278
- I got jjajangmyeon.
- I see.

1159
00:51:46,279 --> 00:51:47,408
I got ramen.

1160
00:51:47,409 --> 00:51:48,479
- Ramen?
- Yes.

1161
00:51:49,279 --> 00:51:50,848
Alaskan pink shrimp avocado tartare?

1162
00:51:50,849 --> 00:51:51,879
(Male customer 2)

1163
00:51:52,279 --> 00:51:53,588
I have no idea what that is.

1164
00:51:53,589 --> 00:51:54,749
- That over there?
- Yes.

1165
00:51:55,219 --> 00:51:57,459
Alaskan pink shrimp avocado tartare?

1166
00:51:58,189 --> 00:51:59,988
I don't order a dish if it has two words...

1167
00:51:59,989 --> 00:52:01,289
- I don't know.
- Same here.

1168
00:52:02,289 --> 00:52:03,359
What a strange menu.

1169
00:52:05,629 --> 00:52:07,499
Are those pickles?

1170
00:52:07,899 --> 00:52:09,768
Avocado?

1171
00:52:09,769 --> 00:52:11,099
