1174
00:52:20,149 --> 00:52:22,379
Kkanpunggi chicken over rice.

1175
00:52:23,979 --> 00:52:26,219
- I'm getting this one.
- Me too.

1176
00:52:28,089 --> 00:52:29,459
We can also get spicy chilli shrimp.

1177
00:52:31,559 --> 00:52:34,329
(The male customers choose Ma Restaurant.)

1178
00:52:34,959 --> 00:52:37,159
(Another male customer)

1179
00:52:38,059 --> 00:52:39,228
