1180
00:52:39,229 --> 00:52:40,299
- Are you okay with it?
- Yes.

1181
00:52:41,169 --> 00:52:42,569
- How about a meal?
- I'm in.

1182
00:52:44,269 --> 00:52:45,469
Would you like to order?

1183
00:52:47,409 --> 00:52:50,639
(The next male customer walks up without hesitation.)

1184
00:52:51,079 --> 00:52:53,809
(Another male customer)

1185
00:52:54,309 --> 00:52:56,879
(Male customers make up 80 percent.)

1186
00:52:58,219 --> 00:53:00,419
We got another order, so that's five in total.

1187
00:53:01,119 --> 00:53:05,259
Remember when I said we'd get a flood of orders all of a sudden?

1188
00:53:05,819 --> 00:53:06,888
Seok Su, we're running...

1189
00:53:06,889 --> 00:53:07,958
- on a system.
- Okay.

1190
00:53:07,959 --> 00:53:09,289
- Give it here, okay?
- Okay.

1191
00:53:09,529 --> 00:53:10,558
Do me a favour.

1192
00:53:10,559 --> 00:53:12,198
Lay out ten and put onions in them.

1193
00:53:12,199 --> 00:53:15,068
(Setting up the soup bowl zone)

1194
00:53:15,069 --> 00:53:16,268
Let's wrap up the soup and kkanpunggi chicken here.

1195
00:53:16,269 --> 00:53:17,339
- Here?
- Yes.

1196
00:53:17,999 --> 00:53:19,638
(Kkanpunggi chicken and soup,)

1197
00:53:19,639 --> 00:53:21,409
(chilli shrimp, fried rice with egg, plating)

1198
00:53:21,969 --> 00:53:23,379
We have to move fast.

1199
00:53:24,379 --> 00:53:26,008
- This is the real deal.
- What?

1200
00:53:26,009 --> 00:53:29,649
If this system fails and we get backed up,

1201
00:53:30,119 --> 00:53:32,079
